snippet.title: Hellblade E3 2015 Trailer
snippet.description:
Hellblade E3 2015 Trailer. Follow the Hellblade journey at Hellblade.com

Hellblade Senua's Sacrifice is releasing August 8th. Pre-order now for $29.99/£24.99/€29.99!

Pre-order for PlayStation 4 |
